            border-left: 4px solid #5CC05C; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
  &lt;strong style="color: #5CC05C;"&gt;Success:&lt;/strong&gt; Message here.
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="padding: 16px; background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
